title: Australian scientist, 104, plans to kill himself with 'Swiss option'
text:
Australian scientist, 104, plans to kill himself with 'Swiss option' 2:41pm IST - 01:11
An 104-year-old Australian scientist travelled to Switzerland to end his life under the nation's liberal assisted suicide laws, although he was not ill. Rough cut (no reporter narration).
